  "merge_notes": "School conflict: 2 ICT vs 1 SMC; picked ICT by majority. The SMC project (Daily Profiles) defines premium specifically for consolidation (Seek and Destroy) mean-reversion, while ICT projects include both bearish bias and bullish expansion contexts. The unified card incorporates both perspectives. The Foundation project's definition was originally in Chinese; translated and merged.",
